column5: My Boy Scout troop just returned from a week trip on Wasaksina and the fishing was excellent. We caught mostly smallies, but the walleyes were biting also. The boys had a great time and the weather was perfect.Scout Master
ScoutMaster, I was wondering how your trip went, glad to hear you and the boys had a good time, and caught fish, did the maps help?email me if you would like.Mike
